* ''{{ill|Tenshoza Ise Nisho Kotai Jingu Go Chinza Shidai Ki|ja|天照坐伊勢二所皇太神宮御鎮座次第記|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshoza Ise Nisho Kotai Jingu Go Chinza Shidai Ki|qq=}}'' ("Account of the Enshrinement of the Two Ise Grand Shrines")
* ''{{ill|Ise Nisho Kotai Jingu Go Chinza Denki|ja|伊勢二所皇太神御鎮座伝記|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ise Nisho Kotai Jingu Go Chinza Denki|qq=}}'' ("Records of the Enshrinement of the Two Ise Grand Shrines")
* ''{{ill|Toyouke Kotai Jingu Go Chinza Honki|ja|豊受皇太神御鎮座本紀|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Toyouke Kotai Jingu Go Chinza Honki|qq=}}'' ("The Fundamental Record of the Enshrinement of Toyouke Grand Shrine")
